{"tid":837197,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iOS12大問題? 用家：更新後屏幕質素變差","createTime":"2018-09-26T07:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T17:09:46.000Z","uid":33357,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5501111b966e633432a331b4893cbcfa2b4b8aff","tid":837197,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:47:05.000Z","msg":"iPhone X update完mon質素退化<br />\n對比色同色彩平衡有偏差<br />\n變白 飽和度降低<br />\nReddit, twitter, MacRumors都有投訴<br />\n前幾日已有國外報導<br />\nupdate前諗清楚先<br />\n<br />\nComplaints about this are spreading fast across with notable hubs on Reddit and the popular MacRumors forum, as well as numerous tweets on Twitter. As one user explained:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The OLED panel on the iPhone X had such wonderful colours and contrast on iOS 11. After the iOS 12 update, the colours and the contrast have been ruined on my iPhone X&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nWhile some of the responses are understandably angry, frustrated and even conspiratorial, the general consensus is summed up by MacRumors forum member &lsquo;magicschoolbus&rsquo; who said when you look at an iPhone display running iOS 12 &ldquo;It just does not look [to be] calibrated correctly.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/gordonkelly/2018/09/22/apple-ios-12-problem-display-iphone-x-xs-ipad-upgrade/#1dfd7a0d364d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fgordonkelly%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2Fapple-ios-12-problem-display-iphone-x-xs-ipad-upgrade%2F%231dfd7a0d364d&d=kfSNCAAQUomQqF8ClgZlJgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=fa0b47db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/gordonkelly/2018/09/22/apple-ios-12-problem-display-iphone-x-xs-ipad-upgrade/#1dfd7a0d364d</a>"},{"pid":"e2a0cbf7d23855a07886df90c3d04e57873597db","tid":837197,"uid":174755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:48:41.000Z","msg":"iphone8呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2ab1bdbd1a8b56344748b5655bae2704bf8736","tid":837197,"uid":23872,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:56:13.000Z","msg":"我都覺update完<br />\nMon既色淡左好多<br />\n連燈完全冇人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fa1cc7faf46c3fff661a454451a51b83c9bd83","tid":837197,"uid":23872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都覺update完<br />\nMon既色淡左好多<br />\n連<del>燈</del>完全冇人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n登"},{"pid":"fb3afb5b6c7a74a03ce17d1ea3783ffd4739aa71","tid":837197,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f2ab1bdbd1a8b56344748b5655bae2704bf8736","tid":837197,"uid":23872,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:56:13.000Z","msg":"我都覺update完<br />\nMon既色淡左好多<br />\n連燈完全冇人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:03:29.000Z","msg":"台灣都係琴日先開始有報<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/amp/story/11017/3386658\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fstory%2F11017%2F3386658&d=kfSNCAAQUomQqF8ClgZlJgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=d2e370c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/amp/story/11017/3386658</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果上週推出最新行動作業系統iOS 12，不少用戶更新後好評不斷，發現效能、速度，以及使用順暢度都大幅提升，不過有商業雜誌調查後發現，iOS 12似乎會破壞螢幕原先應有的顯示品質，尤其使用iPhone X的用戶此情況最嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n根據商業雜誌《富比士》(Forbes)報導，近日有用戶更新至iOS 12作業系統後，發現螢幕顯示功能變差，甚至對比及色彩平衡都出現嚴重錯誤，1名iPhone X的用戶表示，採用OLED螢幕的iPhone X在使用iOS 11系統時，螢幕的色彩平衡與對比都相當完美，不料更新至iOS 12後，「整個螢幕畫質就毀了」。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，早在beta版的iOS 12測試期間，就有部分用戶反應螢幕顯示品質有問題，但並未獲得蘋果官方的重視，導致正式版推出時問題仍存在，有iPhone X的用戶形容，「更新到iOS 12後，iPhone螢幕就像是沒有被正確校正一樣」，抱怨雖然整體系統穩定性相當高，但還是難免會有類似情況發生。"},{"pid":"50552eb99e973040773bf95da2a54a86f2169d71","tid":837197,"uid":35815,"like":10,"dislike":8,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:40:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ec9f35be7d